.DT
comment
Discworld player help
comment

.SH Name
.SI 5
comment - Report a comment, this is a bug that only stays in the
          database for a maximum of one month, no matter what.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
bug replies
bug replies all
bug object <name of NPC or item>
bug command <name>
bug spell <name>
bug spell generic
bug spell new
bug ritual <name>
bug ritual generic
bug ritual new
bug help
bug help <subject>
bug room
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command puts a temporary comment on a room.  A comment should be
used for things like code reviews and anything else that is not an error
and is only a temporary note on a file.
.EP

.SH See also
.SI 5
typo, idea, liaisons, bugcheck, errors
.EI
